# A standalone Scholar Ninja app

Alpha software. May not work at all.

# Running

1. Build with npm run build
2. Run resulting `app.nw` package with node-webkit

# API

This implementation also exposes an API, which you can query like this:
`curl http://localhost:8999/?q=example`

# Can it run headless?

https://github.com/rogerwang/node-webkit/issues/769
